    "name": "Ascend Demo",
    "steam_appid": 2297410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/3aadfb0cdb65823fcdd76aeafcef4803.avif?t=1749505953\" width=616 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve ancient puzzles, collect tarot cards, and complete the zodiac trials to climb the mountain and save your people in Ascend, a 3D puzzle adventure. Shift between Day, Twilight, and Dusk with your Time Turner to reveal secrets, alter the landscape, and discover hidden paths. Will you ascend? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/80348f21139ef60a638704c5a76d077b.avif?t=1749505953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras_big/80348f21139ef60a638704c5a76d077b.avif?t=1749505953 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/96c986a758805126444ab4974ec146b3.poster.avif?t=1749505953\" width=614 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/96c986a758805126444ab4974ec146b3.webm?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/96c986a758805126444ab4974ec146b3.mp4?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To save her people and restore balance to the world, Aurora must do what nobody has ever done before: navigate the zodiac trials to scale the mystical mountain and uncover the secrets of a lost civilisation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each challenge contains a puzzle linked to the constellations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/0b349ac4073a9f0e0127582e98706227.avif?t=1749505953\" width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift between Day, Twilight, and Dusk with the Time Turner. Each time of day has a different effect on the world, revealing secrets, altering the landscape, and opening hidden paths to allow you to solve the puzzles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/8857ba29325094dfb286c4951e827943.poster.avif?t=1749505953\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/8857ba29325094dfb286c4951e827943.webm?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/8857ba29325094dfb286c4951e827943.mp4?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/c309d990f6df3afb653a247bca1e5c6f.avif?t=1749505953\" width=800 height=93 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the mysterious tarot cards across the mountain to learn their secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/7f3d3fe943f13fb6e0b6f2a6e5598fa5.poster.avif?t=1749505953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/7f3d3fe943f13fb6e0b6f2a6e5598fa5.webm?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/7f3d3fe943f13fb6e0b6f2a6e5598fa5.mp4?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/96cb539d991fb15f57cc09c7c17a5d2b.avif?t=1749505953\" width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not the first to attempt this journey. Discover the remnants of past pilgrims, hear their echoes, and uncover the myths that shape your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/6f3d8a8bad42c396b1bd0290b24fb099.poster.avif?t=1749505953\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/6f3d8a8bad42c396b1bd0290b24fb099.webm?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/6f3d8a8bad42c396b1bd0290b24fb099.mp4?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/2128ab01def4b4f98d6b4b4f91571c77.avif?t=1749505953\" width=800 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just as Aurora must overcome her fears and struggles in the trials, many people face their own struggles with mental health. That’s why we’ve partnered with <strong>Safe in Our World</strong>, a charity focused on supporting mental health awareness through video games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/384b2895eb3d2e15c20f6799e4ef310f.poster.avif?t=1749505953\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/384b2895eb3d2e15c20f6799e4ef310f.webm?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297410/extras/384b2895eb3d2e15c20f6799e4ef310f.mp4?t=1749505953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
